f_subheading: A place to connect if you are a spouse, an adult child, a grandchild, a neighbor or a friend.
Although all caregivers face some common issues, there are unique experiences faced by spouses and partners. Here you will find others who share those experiences.

f_heading: I Have Alzheimer’s or Another Dementia
f_subheading: If you have Alzheimer's or another dementia, this forum is for you.
If you are under age 65 and have Alzheimer's disease or another dementia, use this forum to connect with others in the same situation.
